{"tid":2321268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK01：泛民總辭後建制政團評分全跌　謝偉俊民望居首　包尾鄭松泰咁解釋","createTime":"2020-12-11T11:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T11:34:51.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b093c50530da3d0e79bda2a94d2b89e2c18a47ea","tid":2321268,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"民主派總辭後，立法會幾乎清一色是建制派，只餘熱血公民鄭松泰、醫學界陳沛然。香港研究協會發表第六屆立法會延任後首次調查，發現獨立建制派謝偉俊評分位列眾議員之首，以5分為滿分，獲2.78分，評分最低的是新界西的熱血公民鄭松泰，僅得2.02分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5689894/org/7139546413b95bb40c96c8fb3e022678.jpg/HDN63YAIx1TM7R6IIShp9W0swOydVu9h4G_rSOBv60g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5689894%2Forg%2F7139546413b95bb40c96c8fb3e022678.jpg%2FHDN63YAIx1TM7R6IIShp9W0swOydVu9h4G_rSOBv60g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=833110a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝偉俊評分最高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5718268/org/c19e36928b0368f28908c6222d13ac2f.jpg/U11H3gsqP8t1d6-W87HPrlZ5tBVntMGx6NVJ1ejVSdU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5718268%2Forg%2Fc19e36928b0368f28908c6222d13ac2f.jpg%2FU11H3gsqP8t1d6-W87HPrlZ5tBVntMGx6NVJ1ejVSdU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5a1aac8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評分最低的是新界西的熱血公民鄭松泰，得2.02分。（盧翊銘攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201126/408588677317398528749308.jpeg/kMItPfX3kPMbrU_i685hTrCnMbJYi-Ueebne63m53us?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201126%2F408588677317398528749308.jpeg%2FkMItPfX3kPMbrU_i685hTrCnMbJYi-Ueebne63m53us%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=81169b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201118/405690947121188864035479.jpeg/BeNiYS1wyOClGkPiGIIujpFCBpb7l0z7WlcsflpXLH4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201118%2F405690947121188864035479.jpeg%2FBeNiYS1wyOClGkPiGIIujpFCBpb7l0z7WlcsflpXLH4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=12321dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭泳舜、陳恒鑌評分跌幅大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5250456/org/079656e84698c0e55daf7c03194a556b.jpg/Xl-N3tj6NgaXOnL5xIAPG_V8kxrmajEONSgo4zUoKOM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5250456%2Forg%2F079656e84698c0e55daf7c03194a556b.jpg%2FXl-N3tj6NgaXOnL5xIAPG_V8kxrmajEONSgo4zUoKOM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1fa283f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉劉淑儀在香港島續排榜首，（高仲明攝）<br />\n<br />\n研究協會於11月26日至12月8日訪問了1070名市民，就其所屬選區直選和「超級區議會」立法會議員的表現，以及在立法會內擁有議席的9個香港主要政團之支持度進行評分。<br />\n各區排名中，葉劉淑儀在香港島續排榜首，九龍東榜首為謝偉俊，九龍西為梁美芬，新界東為葛珮帆，新界西為麥美娟；「超級區議會」李慧琼的評分則較周浩鼎高。<br />\n在20位繼續履職的地區直選及「超級區議會」議員中，評分下跌的議員有10人，其中民建聯鄭泳舜、陳恒鑌跌幅較大，分別跌0.47分及0.49分。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民評分最低 鄭松泰：一向無留意民調<br />\n政團評分方面，9個在立法會內擁有議席的政團評分悉數下跌，其中熱血公民（2.15分，-0.35分）的評分跌幅最大。擁有13個議席的民建聯以2.44分排在榜首，體育、演藝、文化及出版界議員馬逢國為主席的「新論壇」，則以1.80分排榜末。<br />\n鄭松泰在社交網站回應稱，一向沒留意類似的民意調查，呼籲進行民調的機構「唔好浪費地球資源，為環保盡一分力。」"},{"pid":"d11f4576375f2827fa07bbb485e69e5ef21ff318","tid":2321268,"uid":173459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"唔好客氣 我哋都係做自己嘢<br />\n隻熱狗抵攞咁嘅分"}]}